author: Nerdstalgic
description:
Brooklyn Nine-Nine is one of the most beloved sitcoms of the modern era. Starring Andy Samberg, Terry Crews, Andre Braugher, and Chelsea Peretti, the series delivered eight seasons of laugh-out-loud comedy, heartfelt storytelling, and unforgettable moments.  Brooklyn Nine Nine not only gave us 8 seasons of near perfect television, but told stories that resonate across generations.  

We rank and revisit the highs and lows of Brooklyn Nine-Nine’s incredible run. From its hilarious cold opens to its emotional finales. No doubt, it’s still one of TV’s best comedy ensembles ever.

#brooklynninenine #andysamberg #terrycrews #sitcom
title: Breaking Down The Highs And Lows Of Brooklyn Nine-Nine | Compilation
